{"tid":2393500,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"跟波多野結衣「開房間」5千人湧入引暴動！必須邀請才能進","createTime":"2021-02-03T13:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T14:09:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5615cc140b02a023c66bbaee34cf06483e2367af","tid":2393500,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"這幾天一款神秘語音聊天App「Clubhouse」一夕竄紅，因為要有使用者的「邀請碼」你才能進入使用，而一個使用者最多也只能邀請兩位，兼具稀有和優越感的特色，吸引一堆政商名流、娛樂巨星的加入，昨（2日）日本AV女優波多野結衣都註冊「開房間」，一口氣讓5000人聊天室瞬間滿員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/18/2560708-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F18%2F2560708-PH.jpg&h=4d5a0c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲波多野結衣有「暗黑林志玲」之稱。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n這個Clubhouse App 只能用語音聊天，還不能錄音，吸引一大堆網紅或是聲量高的KOL使用，32歲AV女優波多野結衣，因有「暗黑林志玲」之稱而紅遍大中華，其內地社交網粉絲多達289萬人，疫情前經常穿梭中、港、台跑活動做宣傳，但因疫情影響，工作量銳減，她加入Clubhouse 後，隨即「開設房間」，一瞬間湧入五千位粉絲，癱瘓網路，聊天室直接滿員不給其他人加入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/03/3013543-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2F3013543-PH.jpg&h=187c37ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女優波多野結衣開聊天室，湧進五千人。（圖／翻攝自Clubhouse App）<br />\n<br />\n令人驚訝的是，同一間聊天室裡面，還有其他超大咖AV女優，像是明日花綺羅、資深女優白木優子通通都在裡面，可以同時跟這些女優們用聲音毫無距離的聊天，或是聽著她們美妙的嗓音，讓進不去聊天室房間的粉絲都直呼：「難怪我上不去」、「網路根本塞爆」、「崩潰中卡卡的結束了」、「沒有日文口譯員」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/31/2584770-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F31%2F2584770-PH.jpg&h=6353788f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「暗黑林志玲」之稱的波多野結衣。（圖／翻攝自波多野結衣推特）"},{"pid":"25ca8d43485f570c1f1437a0db361006c0915891","tid":2393500,"uid":4826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"屌那媽，波多野正過林志玲好撚多啦"},{"pid":"416b9339222e4cfcdf5dce56e671b43a4b55d65e","tid":2393500,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:12:49.000Z","msg":"你個死標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4f9ee26223e11322f51dec3fc03e5f4ced94a5","tid":2393500,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ece9b6619be05db97e0a27c1d49865ee842e6e5","tid":2393500,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ca8d43485f570c1f1437a0db361006c0915891","tid":2393500,"uid":4826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"屌那媽，波多野正過林志玲好撚多啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"咪臭撚係<br />\n台灣波多野就啱"},{"pid":"7880a5553cc888f20225ae5047ff7eb9e9c3f7d1","tid":2393500,"uid":59586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"求invite<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d185bb3d5b4d1959ad2ad63e20b0072570c1c93","tid":2393500,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25ca8d43485f570c1f1437a0db361006c0915891","tid":2393500,"uid":4826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"屌那媽，波多野正過林志玲好撚多啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"0x年真係一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f35f2f755e9666c531085dffc67191bc473cba","tid":2393500,"uid":248020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yVbzus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yVbzus.png&h=fd849f1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f79500e5459f2c1335eddedfb8c17c3728716b7a","tid":2393500,"uid":149496,"like":1,"disl